'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun ji tsoron cewa za a yi musu ba'a da 'yan Muppets
Wasu 'yan majalisa na kasa sun ji tsoro game da shawarar da aka yi na canja sunansu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament, dan majalisa na Wales).
Dalilin shi ne, akwai shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa 'Welsh Parliament'.
'Yan majalisa na kasa daga kowane bangare na siyasa suna tsoron zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce kungiyarsa na da damuwa saboda sunan  yana yin waƙa da Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu da ba na Wales ba: A cikin harshen Welsh, twp yana nufin doof da pwp na Aa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya ce dukan jam'iyyar ba ta yi farin ciki ba kuma ta ba da shawarwari.
Wani memba na jam'iyyar Conservative Party ta Wales ya ce kungiyarsa tana shirye ta sake suna amma ya nuna kamanceceniya tsakanin MWP da Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta harafin Welsh w kamar harafin u a Turanci da ake magana da shi a Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar, wadda ke tsara dokar sauya sunayen, ta ce: "Hakika, 'yan majalisar ne suke da ikon yanke shawara game da sunayen mambobin majalisar".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Tarayyar Wales ta canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon wani taron jama'a kan shawarwarin da suka nuna goyon baya ga sunan Welsh Parliament ga majalisar kasa.
Game da taken mambobin majalisar, kwamitin ya fi son Welsh Parliament Members ko WMPs, yayin da a cikin wani taron jama'a, zaɓi MWP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya.
'Yan majalisar dokokin kasar na nuna cewa suna ba da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma gwagwarmayar samun yarjejeniya na iya zama matsala ga shugaban kasa Elin Jones, wanda za ta gabatar da wani kudiri cikin makonni.
Dokar gyare-gyare za ta ƙunshi wasu canje-canje game da yadda majalisar ke aiki, ciki har da dokoki game da rashin cancantar membobin majalisar da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisar za su iya yin kuri'ar karshe a kan sunansu a lokacin da suke muhawara kan dokar.
'Yan Macedonia sun amince da sauya sunan kasar a wata kuri'ar raba gardama
