Shugaban kasar Mexico wanda aka zaba Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja kan fararen hula ba, yayin da ake gabatowar cika shekaru 50 da kisan gilla da aka yi wa dalibai a kasarsa.
