Kuma yanzu shafi daga littafinmu na "Sunday Morning" a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka shige, an haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wanda hakan ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama sanannen abu a kimiyya, kuma ya zama sanannen abu a al'adun gargajiya, misali a cikin fim din 1950 Bells of Coronado tare da masu neman ilimin kimiyyar cowboy Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers:  Wannan na'urar Geiger ne da ake amfani da ita wajen neman ma'adanai masu hasken rana kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin radiyo a cikin ma'adanai.
