A yanzu al'ada ce a duba duk wani sabon fim da aka yi da launi na Burtaniya don neman nassoshin Brexit. Wannan kuma ya zama gaskiya ga wannan farfadowar fim din satar fim na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 da Johnny English da The Spy Who Kaddamar da Shi, kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 da Johnny English da kuma Now.
Shin yin maganganun wulakanci game da kanmu game da yadda muke da wauta zai zama sabon damar fitarwa ga al'ummarmu?
A kowane hali, an sake ba da lasisin Johnny English mai ƙyalli, mai ƙyalli, kuma marar iyawa don ya ɓata, kuma sunansa ya nuna fiye da kowane abu cewa yana da wani abu mai ban dariya ga masu kallo a cikin duniya da ba ta magana da harshen Turanci ba.
Hakika, shi ne wani dan leken asiri mai ban mamaki wanda yake ganin kansa mai ban sha'awa ne kuma mai son duniya, amma a gaskiya shi wani abu ne na Clouseau, wani ɗan Mr. Bean, da kuma wani ɗan ƙaramin ɗan adam wanda ya ba da rawa guda ɗaya ga waƙar "The Hour of the Winner" a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na 2012 a London.
