Wannan sabon abu na Johnny English yana da wasu lokuta masu kyau.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English a cikin makamai na dā yana zuwa wurin wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu, kuma yana da ɗan ƙaramin ƙyalle a kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana da baiwa ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma abin dariya yana da rauni kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman saboda jerin fina-finai masu mahimmanci kamar 007 da Mission Impossible sun ba da abubuwan ban dariya.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, rashin jin daɗin Johnny English ba shi da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din da aka yi da Bean.
