Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma an taimaka wajen rage talauci a wannan bikin?
A wannan Asabar, bikin Global Citizen Festival yana faruwa a New York, bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara tare da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa  don magance talauci a duniya.
Dubun dubatan mutane za su halarci bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka gudanar a karo na bakwai a wannan shekara, ba wai kawai don ganin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci zuwa 2030.
