Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda hukumomi suka ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda matsalar sadarwa, masu ba da agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya kuma yana kan iyakar bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala gundumar gwamnati ce da ke arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi a kan wani yanki na bakin teku mai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 mil).
A cikin gundumar gwamnati, wani yanki na yanki a ƙarƙashin lardin, an kiyasta mutane 299,200 ne ke zaune a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana kuma hakar nickel a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya afkawa Donggala ta Yamma a shekarar 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Ƙasar Indonesiya tana kan yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a ƙasar.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan tekun Indiya, kusan rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra tsakanin ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya kai ga gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta girgiza ɗaya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai da ke gaɓar teku na Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai saurin girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, ya haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunatar da su game da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Wannan lokacin ba a yi tsunami ba, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, wanda ya shahara ga masu yawon buɗe ido, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun kasance a kan tsibirin na ɗan lokaci.
