An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot a wani harin ta'addanci, inda a watan Oktoba ya yi tsere a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu keke.
