"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, da kuma wasu matsaloli da kuma asarar rayukansu", in ji sanarwar.
