An kuma ga wani ruwan sama mai ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan taro a ko kusa da gabar ruwan Pinellas, low zuwa high a ko kusa da gabar ruwan Manatee, background zuwa high a ko kusa da gabar ruwan Charlotte, background zuwa high a ko kusa da gabar ruwan Lee, da low a ko kusa da gabar ruwan Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni na ciwon numfashi a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani sabon yanayin numfashi da aka samu a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
